name: Planetfall (itch) (Jacic)
description:
Portal-Tech maintains their wormhole technology is state of the art.  A safe and reliable way to travel between the stars...

But you know better.

Stranded on an alien world, can you avoid the unknown dangers and make it back to civilisation?

A micro interactive fiction piece written for the 2019 Sub-Q Jam with the theme of "Environment".
